      "title": "8 unions strike for two days",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Eight health unions, including public health inspectors, will go on strike tomorrow (29) and the next day (30) due to the current fuel crisis, said Ubul Rohana, chairman of the public health union."
